[ Applause ]

00:17:36.336 --> 00:17:38.436
Now, we absolutely love this

00:17:38.436 --> 00:17:40.316
game because it captures the

00:17:40.316 --> 00:17:41.476
magic of time.

00:17:42.216 --> 00:17:44.266
Have you ever wanted to travel

00:17:44.266 --> 00:17:46.346
back in time, or maybe just

00:17:46.546 --> 00:17:47.596
relive a moment that you

00:17:47.596 --> 00:17:48.306
reminisce about?

00:17:49.106 --> 00:17:50.786
Well, technology hasn't quite

00:17:50.786 --> 00:17:52.836
gotten us there yet, but playing

00:17:52.836 --> 00:17:54.256
this game gives you a sense of

00:17:54.256 --> 00:17:55.526
what that might be like.

00:17:56.506 --> 00:17:58.356
And you play as these two main

00:17:58.356 --> 00:18:00.636
characters, named Arina and

00:18:00.716 --> 00:18:00.916
Frendt.

00:18:02.246 --> 00:18:04.016
This game tells a special story

00:18:04.016 --> 00:18:05.066
about friendship, and we

00:18:05.286 --> 00:18:06.366
absolutely love it for its

00:18:06.436 --> 00:18:07.976
cinematic moments and its

00:18:07.976 --> 00:18:09.146
immersive experience.

00:18:09.796 --> 00:18:11.426
Let's take a closer look.

00:18:11.786 --> 00:18:12.976
T.C.?

00:18:13.516 --> 00:18:18.146
[ Music ]

00:18:18.646 --> 00:18:20.836
>> Let's have a moment to take

00:18:20.836 --> 00:18:21.756
in this whole island.

00:18:23.956 --> 00:18:25.886
Now, beyond the stunning imagery

00:18:25.886 --> 00:18:28.256
that you see, what really

00:18:28.256 --> 00:18:29.756
impressed us about this game is

00:18:29.756 --> 00:18:31.226
that this kind of attention to

00:18:31.226 --> 00:18:33.696
detail actually extends to its

00:18:33.696 --> 00:18:35.286
bespoke soundtrack, its

00:18:35.286 --> 00:18:37.236
natural-feeling haptics, and

00:18:37.236 --> 00:18:38.746
more than that, the

00:18:38.746 --> 00:18:40.486
storytelling.

00:18:40.486 --> 00:18:42.246
Notice how Frendt is taken aback

00:18:42.246 --> 00:18:43.716
when Arina's able to walk over

00:18:43.716 --> 00:18:45.896
the clouds, and then he catches

00:18:45.896 --> 00:18:47.716
up, still a little unsure.

00:18:47.716 --> 00:18:50.396
And here, I just stopped time,

00:18:50.496 --> 00:18:52.636
and I do that by just not

00:18:52.636 --> 00:18:54.456
tapping anything.

00:18:54.456 --> 00:18:55.616
This means that I'm never

00:18:55.616 --> 00:18:57.696
feeling rushed or under any kind

00:18:57.696 --> 00:18:58.316
of time pressure.

00:18:58.466 --> 00:19:01.066
We think this game play mechanic

00:19:01.066 --> 00:19:05.126
is really simple, yet effective.

00:19:05.156 --> 00:19:06.196
Now, because you move both

00:19:06.196 --> 00:19:07.936
characters at once, and only

00:19:07.936 --> 00:19:09.986
control the flow of time, an

00:19:09.986 --> 00:19:11.426
interesting interplay happens

00:19:11.426 --> 00:19:13.876
between the two characters.

