Here, you will notice that Arina

00:19:16.396 --> 00:19:18.056
is no longer able to move any

00:19:18.056 --> 00:19:20.126
more forward in time, and that's

00:19:20.206 --> 00:19:21.506
because Frendt has fallen

00:19:21.506 --> 00:19:22.000
behind.

00:19:22.726 --> 00:19:24.796
So let's go back in time, and

00:19:24.846 --> 00:19:26.006
see what we can do differently

00:19:26.006 --> 00:19:27.536
to help him out.

