Now, you might notice that with

00:19:29.626 --> 00:19:31.096
each time I hop over the saw

00:19:31.096 --> 00:19:33.046
handle, it continues to cut

00:19:33.046 --> 00:19:34.436
through the plank.

00:19:34.436 --> 00:19:36.506
So let me go back and forth in

00:19:36.506 --> 00:19:37.406
time a few times.

