We're going with one of my

00:22:24.336 --> 00:22:25.616
personal favorites, the Chevy

00:22:25.666 --> 00:22:27.636
Camaro, and of course, we had to

00:22:27.636 --> 00:22:28.296
make it purple.

00:22:30.076 --> 00:22:31.766
With 70 courses spanning the

00:22:31.766 --> 00:22:33.366
globe, from Cairo to the

00:22:33.366 --> 00:22:34.906
Himalayas, today, we're going to

00:22:34.946 --> 00:22:36.046
be racing the streets of

00:22:36.046 --> 00:22:37.000
Shanghai.

00:22:38.466 --> 00:22:40.000
All right, here we go.

